le, auditable, and bounded.\n\nThat is the scaffolding we actually want: not a world without betrayal, but a world where fewer betrayals become permanent.\n```", "tool_call_id": null, "tool_calls": null, "tool_name": null, "timestamp": 1777222684.0993104, "token_count": null, "finish_reason": "stop", "reasoning": null, "reasoning_details": null, "codex_reasoning_items": null}]}
