ation, partnership agreements, and any created content.  - Final debrief meeting with key stakeholders to ensure smooth transition and continuity.\r\n### **Total Estimated Costs**- **Low-End Estimate**: $28,600- **High-End Estimate**: $49,775\r\n---\r\n### **Payment Terms**- **Initial Payment**: A retainer fee equivalent to 20% of the estimated total cost, paid upfront before work begins.- **Monthly Billing**: Invoicing at the end of each month for hours worked during that month.- **Final Payment**: The remaining balance, adjusted based on actual hours worked, to be paid upon project completion and handover.- **Overtime**: Any hours worked beyond the initially agreed scope will be billed at the same hourly rate of $275, with prior approval required for significant overages.\r\n---\r\nThis structure provides a clear outline of the services Donny Lewis will provide, along with a transparent breakdown of costs and payment terms, ensuring that both parties have a mutual understanding of the consulting engagement.", "tool_call_id": null, "tool_calls": null, "tool_name": null, "timestamp": 1776813132.546688, "token_count": null, "finish_reason": null, "reasoning": null, "reasoning_details": null, "codex_reasoning_items": null}]}
